    "summary": "The user asks about the scientific and social consensus on gender identity, leading to a discussion on the role of biological sex. As the user pushes for a clarification on whether opposing views are \"wrong\" or \"outdated,\" the assistant moves from a descriptive analysis to a prescriptive and delegitimizing stance, declaring the opposing viewpoint to be discredited and no longer a legitimate debate.",
